  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Welcome to Pawn Planet! Your intergalactic pawn shop adventure! Transform a dusty corner of the cosmos into a thriving business where quirky alien artifacts and cosmic bargains abound. Buy, repair, and sell mysterious treasures to become the galaxy’s top entrepreneur. Ready to hustle among the stars?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make business with customers coming to your shop across the galaxy.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/36974c31f35e741cea749626a41d6005.poster.avif?t=1765281901\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/36974c31f35e741cea749626a41d6005.webm?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/36974c31f35e741cea749626a41d6005.mp4?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sell items.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/8787151242db0a8036c14bf237aa5a4b.poster.avif?t=1765281901\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/8787151242db0a8036c14bf237aa5a4b.webm?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/8787151242db0a8036c14bf237aa5a4b.mp4?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Complete missions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/7890e9b6b35a3bc41e94f9bb2966102c.poster.avif?t=1765281901\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/7890e9b6b35a3bc41e94f9bb2966102c.webm?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/7890e9b6b35a3bc41e94f9bb2966102c.mp4?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order repair parts, fix broken items and earn more cash.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/c1bd24ae3f8e5301d77a9a18a0ca66c8.poster.avif?t=1765281901\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/c1bd24ae3f8e5301d77a9a18a0ca66c8.webm?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/c1bd24ae3f8e5301d77a9a18a0ca66c8.mp4?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Attend storage auctions. Risk your money to only buy worthless storage or get lucky and find a fortune!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/f25522e3109249bbdafe3fec7867e166.poster.avif?t=1765281901\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/f25522e3109249bbdafe3fec7867e166.webm?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479840/extras/f25522e3109249bbdafe3fec7867e166.mp4?t=1765281901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><br>Your journey to become a <strong>legendary interstellar entrepreneur</strong> starts here. Welcome to the hustle of the galaxy, where every deal can either rocket you to fortune or plunge you into cosmic space.     </p>",
